			title: "Town Hall"
			icon: "minecolonies:blockHutTownHall"
			description: [
				"§6The Town Hall§f is the administrative center of your colony."
				"§fWithout it, nothing else can be built or managed."
				""
				"§ePlacing it:§r"
				"§7• §eGet it§7 from the Supply Camp chest (placed in the founding quest)."
				"§7• §ePlace it§7 on flat ground in the center of your planned colony."
				"§7• §eRight-click§7 → Build → select §eTier 1§7 to begin construction."
				"§7• The Builder must build it — have the Builder's Hut ready first."
				""
				"§eTown Hall interface:§r"
				"§7• §eManage§7 citizens, permissions, colony name, and borders."
				"§7• §eUpgrade§7 from T1 to T5 to increase citizen cap."
				"§7  T1=8 citizens, T2=16, T3=24, T4=32, T5=40."
				"§7• §eAll family members§7: right-click → Join Colony."
				""
				"§a► Claim the Town Hall from the Supply Chest and hold it."
			]
			dependencies: ["00110001"]
		}

		{
			x: 0.0d
