			description: [
				"§6The Builder§f constructs §eevery§f building in your colony."
				"§fWithout a Builder's Hut, nothing can be built. This is always first."
				""
				"§ePlacing and using:§r"
				"§7• §eGet it§7 from the Supply Camp chest."
				"§7• §ePlace§7 it in an accessible spot — the Builder walks to each site."
				"§7• §eRight-click§7 → Build → Tier 1."
				"§7• Once built, hire a citizen as Builder (right-click → Hire)."
				"§7• Order other buildings and the Builder will construct them."
				""
				"§eBuilder tips:§r"
				"§7• §eKeep the Warehouse stocked§7 — Builders pull all materials from it."
				"§7• §eBuild multiple Builder's Huts§7 for parallel construction (recommended)."
				"§7• §eUpgrade Builder's Hut§7 to T5 for faster construction speed."
				""
				"§a► Claim the Builder's Hut from the Supply Chest and hold it."
			]
			dependencies: ["00110002"]
