				"§6The Warehouse§f is the colony's central storage."
				"§fAll citizens pull materials from it, and all production goes into it."
				"§fIt is the colony's lifeblood."
				""
				"§ePlacing and stocking:§r"
				"§7• §ePlace§7 near the colony center — Couriers deliver to and from it."
				"§7• §eRight-click§7 → Build → hire a Warehouse manager."
				"§7• §eDeposit building materials§7 (wood, stone, iron) into the Warehouse."
				"§7  Builders automatically pull what they need."
				""
				"§eCreate supply line (Ch 6.3):§r"
				"§7• §eMechanical Arm§7 delivering directly to the Warehouse block"
