				""
				"§eGetting your first 5 citizens:§r"
				"§7• §eCitizen Huts§7 spawn one citizen each when fully built."
				"§7  Build at least §e5 Citizen Huts§7 to get 5 citizens."
				"§7• §eAlternatively§7: the Supply Camp spawns 2 starter citizens."
				"§7  Add 3 more via Citizen Huts."
				"§7• §eTown Hall T2§7 is needed to raise the citizen cap above 8."
				""
				"§eManaging citizens:§r"
